<item>
<title>1.5.1 - Fixed some bugs and introduced some more</title>
<pubDate>Fri, 18 Sep 2019 21:33:06 -0700</pubDate>
<sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>10.14</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
<description><![CDATA[<h2>Known Issues</h2><ul><li>Your preferences screen for Dynamic Dark Mode might be completely blank</li></ul><h2>What's New | <a href="https://github.com/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/blob/1.5.1/CHANGELOG.md">changelog</a></h2><ul><li>¡Hola! We now have Spanish translation, thanks to<a class="user-mention"data-hovercard-type="user"data-hovercard-url="/hovercards?user_id=9949555"data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click"data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self"href="https://github.com/nununoisy">@nununoisy</a></li><li>You can now skip the setup process and we'll prompt for permissions later (<a class="issue-link js-issue-link"data-error-text="Failed to load issue title"data-id="493637689"data-permission-text="Issue title is private"data-url="https://github.com/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/issues/75"data-hovercard-type="issue"data-hovercard-url="/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/issues/75/hovercard"href="https://github.com/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/issues/75">#75</a>, not fixed)</li><li>The app no longer reschedules at when you switch connection to an expensive/low data network</li><li>If you have found we displaying wrong schedule mode, it should now be fixed</li><li>We no longer attempt an appearance update when your screen updates but not its brightness</li><li>When reopening the app during setup process, we won't show the preferences screen (<a class="issue-link js-issue-link"data-error-text="Failed to load issue title"data-id="493637689"data-permission-text="Issue title is private"data-url="https://github.com/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/issues/75"data-hovercard-type="issue"data-hovercard-url="/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/issues/75/hovercard"href="https://github.com/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/issues/75">#75</a>)</li></ul><p><a href="https://crowdin.com/project/dynamic-dark-mode/invite?d=5545k4f6m6k59393g48373u2i473q4i4l4l4j4s223f4n49353e3n45353d30343a31353t663q483a38373"rel="nofollow">Help translate Dynamic Dark Mode</a> | <a href="https://www.producthunt.com/posts/dynamic-dark-mode"rel="nofollow">Upvote on Product Hunt</a></p>]]></description>
