</item>
<item>
<title>1.5.0 - Black Magic SkyLight</title>
<pubDate>Wed, 14 Sep 2019 07:45:47 -0400</pubDate>
<sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>10.14</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
<description><![CDATA[<h2>Known Issues</h2><ul><li>May display seemingly infinitely many“timed out” prompts under some circumstances, such as when connected to a network that requires authentication through captive portal</li></ul><h2>What's New | <a href="https://github.com/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/blob/1.5.0/CHANGELOG.md">changelog</a></h2><ul><li>Fixed a problem where your dynamic wallpaper may not be updating</li><li>We reduced attempts to switch to the automatic appearance when it's not necessary to do so. (<a class="issue-link js-issue-link"data-error-text="Failed to load issue title"data-id="490719265"data-permission-text="Issue title is private"data-url="https://github.com/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/issues/73"data-hovercard-type="issue"data-hovercard-url="/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/issues/73/hovercard"href="https://github.com/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/issues/73">#73</a>, <a class="issue-link js-issue-link"data-error-text="Failed to load issue title"data-id="414901042"data-permission-text="Issue title is private"data-url="https://github.com/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/issues/57"data-hovercard-type="issue"data-hovercard-url="/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/issues/57/hovercard"href="https://github.com/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/issues/57">#57</a>)</li><li>If you are on macOS Catalina and using Auto appearance by Apple, this is what you'll see: (<a class="issue-link js-issue-link"data-error-text="Failed to load issue title"data-id="491794027"data-permission-text="Issue title is private"data-url="https://github.com/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/issues/74"data-hovercard-type="issue"data-hovercard-url="/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/issues/74/hovercard"href="https://github.com/ApolloZhu/Dynamic-Dark-Mode/issues/74">#74</a>)</li></ul><p><a target="_blank"rel="noopener noreferrer"href="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10842684/64907719-31dcd180-d6c4-11e9-8103-0931d23a7909.png"><img width="637"alt="support for macOS Catalina Auto appearance"src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10842684/64907719-31dcd180-d6c4-11e9-8103-0931d23a7909.png"style="max-width:100%;"></a></p><p><a href="https://crowdin.com/project/dynamic-dark-mode/invite?d=5545k4f6m6k59393g48373u2i473q4i4l4l4j4s223f4n49353e3n45353d30343a31353t663q483a38373"rel="nofollow">Help translate Dynamic Dark Mode</a> | <a href="https://www.producthunt.com/posts/dynamic-dark-mode"rel="nofollow">Upvote on Product Hunt</a></p>]]></description>
